                      <td valign="top" height="100%"><font face="verdana" size="2" color="white"><span class="spnMessageText" id="msg"> I use Splurt, its almost a free 2k of damage (250 mana or so?).  I also use it to time ED.<br /><br />I pull with Dark, then BoT, then pet.  Horror, then Splurt.  SK when appropriate.<br /><br />Never loose aggro.<br /><br />On long pulls (I like to kite on one side only) I pull with Splurt, then ED when back where I want him.<br /><br />On Sentries, pull with SK, you can hit Horror or BoT or SK in the corners.<br /><br />/shrug<br /><br />To me, Splurt is free damage, plus a timer.</span id="msg"></font></td>
